                    <lb n="6"/>kumārar pommunāyakkar A<unclear>ṭ</unclear>ai<unclear>y</unclear>a vaḷaiñcāṉa taḷavicai paṭuppittār <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
                </p>
                
